						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 5 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold deposited with the <hi rend="italic">Tiruvādirai-Gaṇapperumakkaḷ</hi> (committee) at Tiruchcheṅgōḍu for feeding with the interest thereon five Brāhmaṇas (on the day of Tiruvādirai every month), by <hi rend="bold">Kāḍaṉ Pūdi Māṇikkam</hi> in the name of his daughter <hi rend="bold">Muṇḍaṅkōṉ.</hi></p>						

